## Commit conventions

| Prefix | Effect |
|--------|--------|
| `feat:` | minor release |
| `fix:`, `perf:` | patch release |
| `BREAKING CHANGE` footer | major release |
| `refactor:`, `docs:`, `chore:`, `ci:`, `test:` | no release |

Never manually tag releases or edit CHANGELOG.md.
